# Description of data

- The training set is made up of satellite image croppings of PSUs.

--

- Information for labeling is available from 3 surveys.

--

- ~**1800 images** for training (and testing).

--

- Some example images:

--

low stratum PSU:

.center[<img src="imagenes/bajo_1.jpg" width="350">]

